channel.title: Zenith - Grand Exchange bugged!
channel.description:
Recently, I've created a Zenith based server and everything was going well until I found out I couldn't sell anything. Grand Exchange is everything to any user. Users will need the G.E in order to gain money without any problems. I'm asking you all out there reading this, if you have any idea how to help me fix it then please come forward and tell me how here!
[i][b]Thanks, guys! Daniel[/b][/i]
